        <div class="section-title"><h2>Our Story</h2></div>
        <div class="about">
            <img src="images/comany.png" alt="Company">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h3>Founded in 1998</h3>
                <p>We began our journey in 2010 with humble beginnings in Hyderabad, Sindh, taking on small residential and commercial construction projects. What started as a dedicated team of just 8-10 engineers and technicians has now grown into a powerful organization with more than 550 highly skilled professionals working across major cities including Hyderabad, Karachi, Lahore, Islamabad, and Faisalabad.</p>
                <p>Over the past 15+ years, we have successfully executed more than 220 projects, covering a total constructed area of over 8 million square feet. Our portfolio includes landmark residential societies, modern office complexes, large-scale industrial facilities, healthcare centers, educational campuses, government infrastructure, and solar-integrated smart buildings. Each project reflects our core promise: uncompromising quality, strict safety standards, timely completion, and maximum value for our clients.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    <!-- TEAM - Updated with side arrows slider -->
